3) Q: How did you optimize Angular performance?

Answer:

In our project, performance was important because we had large data and multiple API calls.

To improve performance, we used:

- Lazy loading to reduce initial bundle size
- trackBy in ngFor to avoid unnecessary re-rendering
- OnPush change detection for better rendering performance
- Debounce in search APIs
- Pagination instead of loading huge data
- Async pipe to reduce manual subscriptions

These improvements helped reduce UI lag and improve loading speed.

