7. Differenc b/w Promise and Observable
| Feature   | Promise                | Observable                                   |
| --------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| Value     | Returns a single value | Can emit multiple values over time           |
| Execution | Executes immediately   | Lazy execution (starts only when subscribed) |
| Cancel    | Cannot be cancelled    | Can be cancelled using `unsubscribe()`       |


